PN,36601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774293066
OL,3,CRapist whose victim later died jailed
OL,4,C40 years after attack
OL,6,FA rapist whose victim "spiralled" and
OL,7,Fdied before he was brought to justice
OL,8,Fhas been jailed - more than 40 years
OL,9,Fafter the attack.
OL,11,FDavid Hill, now 75, sexually assaulted
OL,12,Fthe 27-year-old woman at knifepoint in
OL,13,Fan underground car park in Sheffield
OL,14,Fin September 1985.
OL,16,FShe died 12 years later but it was not
OL,17,Funtil 2021 that DNA evidence gathered
OL,18,Fat the time of the incident was linked
OL,19,Fto Hill after he was arrested for a
OL,20,Fpublic order offence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774293066
OL,3,CRapist whose victim later died jailed
OL,4,C40 years after attack
OL,6,FHill, of Broom Valley Road, Rotherham,
OL,7,Fwas convicted of rape last month after
OL,8,Fprosecutors were given permission to
OL,9,Fuse the woman's original testimony at
OL,10,Fhis trial.
OL,12,FJailing him for 15 years Judge Peter
OL,13,FHampton told him: "While you have gone
OL,14,Funpunished for many years, she
OL,15,Fsuffered with the damage done before
OL,16,Fher death.
OL,18,F"You have never shown one shred of
OL,19,Fremorse."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774293066
OL,3,CRapist whose victim later died jailed
OL,4,C40 years after attack
OL,6,FRetired detective Robert Varey, who
OL,7,Fwas part of the original investgation,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I am delighted that someone has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed for this absolutely
OL,10,Fhorrendous offence and my thoughts
OL,11,Fremain with the victim's loved ones."
OL,13,FSenior Crown prosecutor Caroline
OL,14,FDeacon added: "I hope this case
OL,15,Fdemonstrates the CPS will always seek
OL,16,Fjustice for rape victims, no matter
OL,17,Fthe circumstances or passage of time."
OL,19,FForced to undress
OL,26,@vD@OOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774293066
OL,3,CRapist whose victim later died jailed
OL,4,C40 years after attack
OL,6,FHill attacked his victim as she was
OL,7,Freturning to her car after spending a
OL,8,Fnight with friends at Josephine's
OL,9,Fnightclub in Sheffield.
OL,11,FHe approached her from behind, held a
OL,12,Fknife to her throat and ordered her to
OL,13,Fundress before attacking her.
OL,15,FThe victim's husband at the time spoke
OL,16,Fof how she arrived home visibly
OL,17,Fdistressed and eventually divulged
OL,18,Fthat she had been raped.
OL,20,FDespite an extensive police
OL,21,Finvestigation, no-one was arrested.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774293066
OL,3,CRapist whose victim later died jailed
OL,4,C40 years after attack
OL,6,FMr Varey said: "I can always remember
OL,7,Fthe case, the distinctive turquoise
OL,8,Fdress she was wearing and how
OL,9,Fdistressed she was.
OL,11,F"Rapes committed by a stranger are
OL,12,Fthankfully rare so this was
OL,13,Finvestigated as a major incident.
OL,15,F"At the time there was not as much
OL,16,FCCTV in the city centre so the car
OL,17,Fpark was not covered and the DNA
OL,18,Fdatabase didn't exist, so
OL,19,Funfortunately the case remained
OL,20,Fundetected."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774293066
OL,3,CRapist whose victim later died jailed
OL,4,C40 years after attack
OL,6,F'Exceptional legal challenges'
OL,8,FThe case was reopened in 2021 after
OL,9,Fscientists conducted a DNA search on a
OL,10,Fsample taken from the victim's
OL,11,Fclothing.
OL,13,FThe search returned a full DNA profile
OL,14,Fmatching Hill, who was arrested in
OL,15,FMarch 2022.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774293066
OL,3,CRapist whose victim later died jailed
OL,4,C40 years after attack
OL,6,FDave Stopford, of the South Yorkshire
OL,7,FPolice cold case team, said: "(Hill)
OL,8,Fcommitted a horrendous crime against a
OL,9,Fstranger, not a care in the world
OL,10,Fabout how that would affect her and to
OL,11,Fbring him to justice is what the aim
OL,12,Fof our department is. When we went and
OL,13,Fknocked on his door he looked
OL,14,Fsurprise."
OL,26,@oD@_pmoD@dpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774293066
OL,3,CRapist whose victim later died jailed
OL,4,C40 years after attack
OL,6,FHill denied the allegation, claiming
OL,7,Fhe could not recall his whereabouts on
OL,8,Fthe night of the attack. But he
OL,9,Fadmitted being a regular at
OL,10,FJosephine's nightclub and engaging in
OL,11,Fcasual sexual encounters, including
OL,12,Fwith married women.
OL,14,FMs Deacon described the case as "among
OL,15,Fthe most complex and unique" she had
OL,16,Fworked on and one with "exceptional
OL,17,Flegal challenges".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774293066
OL,3,CRapist whose victim later died jailed
OL,4,C40 years after attack
OL,6,FShe said: "We successfully applied for
OL,7,Fher original account of the attack to
OL,8,Fbe used in court, even though she has
OL,9,Fnow passed away, ensuring that her
OL,10,Fvoice could be heard after four
OL,11,Fdecades.
OL,13,F"We also applied for medical history,
OL,14,Fshowing she had spoken of the impact
OL,15,Fof the rape on her life with medical
OL,16,Fprofessionals years after it took
OL,17,Fplace, to be shown to the jury.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774293066
OL,3,CRapist whose victim later died jailed
OL,4,C40 years after attack
OL,6,F"David Hill subjected the victim to a
OL,7,Fterrifying and degrading attack that
OL,8,Fcast a shadow over the rest of her
OL,9,Flife."
OL,11,FIn a statement read in court, the
OL,12,Fwoman's brother said she never
OL,13,Frecovered.
OL,15,F"Depression and the rape left her a
OL,16,Fshadow of her previously good-humoured
OL,17,Fformer self," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774293066
OL,3,CRapist whose victim later died jailed
OL,4,C40 years after attack
OL,6,FThe judge said: "Following the attack
OL,7,Fher life spiralled out of control. She
OL,8,Fsimply could not cope with her health
OL,9,Fissues.
OL,11,F"I have information from a number of
OL,12,Fsources that (victim) was a popular,
OL,13,Foutgoing sociable person, well-liked
OL,14,Fby those who knew her. She had lots of
OL,15,Ffriends. She was a hardworking and
OL,16,Fsuccessful woman.
OL,18,F"Sadly she was never the same after
OL,19,Fthe attack.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774293066
OL,3,CRapist whose victim later died jailed
OL,4,C40 years after attack
OL,6,F"Her friend said she went from a
OL,7,Fbubbly happy person to a shell of a
OL,8,Fperson - a living skeleton. She
OL,9,Feffectively withdrew from life and her
OL,10,Fhealth deteriorated to such and extent
OL,11,Fthat she passed away aged 39."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
